vim installation
============================================

NERDTree
---
copy NERDTree plugin into ~/.vim
:NERDTreeToggle

Terminal
---
Base16-Brewer

add a .vimrc file in ~ directory and configue as follows:
---
set number
syntax on
color slate 
set tabstop=4
set autoindent
set noexpandtab
set softtabstop=4
autocmd vimenter * NERDTree

